name: Still Life 1.1, 2021
description: Fizz Pop (b.1974)   Still Life 1.1, 2021   4200 x 3300 pixels      Specially created to be the first limited edition NFT to be minted on hic et nunc; this still life painting is composed of nine unique flowers, from the Library of Elements collection developed on opensea.  Fizz Pop's digital works have a unique and recognizable pop-up-book style aesthetic, exploring contemporary still life and landscape painting today.
